textAfterTable: 15 Songs Customer Reviews Electric!!!           by Society5 Parralox has done what few artist have been able to accomplish in the last several years which is that they put together an excellent and cohesive album. Every single track is outstanding and could be a hit. They deserve serious recognition for their work. I really enjoy their unique sound. Obviously their sound is rooted in the 80’s, but there are so many additional elements in the music that make it new and exciting. The best way I can describe their sound is that if Madonna, The Human League, Information Society, and Goldfrapp all got together and collaborated on an album, it would sound like Electricity. Electricity is definitely worth buying if you want to hear something fresh. Great Sound!           by OTRD85 I heard about Parralox online, and I have to say I'm quite impressed.
